{"tid":271101,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"( 長 ) 從金庸角度睇林敏聰事件","createTime":"2017-06-04T20:24:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-05T19:33:32.000Z","uid":2719,"like":32,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"200900f58f4231981bdf99cfd790150dbcf7651f","tid":271101,"uid":2719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:24:27.000Z","msg":"好多連登仔笑佢無料扮大袋<br />\n又用佢同林夕比乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n其實都難怪 <br />\n睇dse/交配post多到咁<br />\n都知連登一早充斥晒小學雞/mk/5p<br />\n無常識一尾話神化古人都情有可原<br />\n<br />\n其實<br />\n林敏聰有無料<br />\n唔係你班智將講就算 成就反映一切<br />\n四大天王我諗你地識啦<br />\n咁四大填詞人你地又有無聽過<br />\n林就佔其一<br />\n<br />\n就好似金庸咁 東南西北 <br />\n四絕你做到其一 都肯定係神級<br />\n<br />\n但過二三十年後 無人識都正常 <br />\n因為已經隔兩代 郭靖都已經係郭伯伯<br />\n啲後生都興吹捧神鵰俠<br />\n<br />\n跟住就有班小學雞話<br />\n邊撚個黃藥師 無人識你喎<br />\n唔理禮法以為自己好型 <br />\n仲講咪楊過打撚死你啦<br />\n<br />\n其實你地有諗楊過<br />\n都係佢嘅後後輩<br />\n東邪收山 到郭紅 先到楊<br />\n楊自己都唔敢話黃垃圾廢老<br />\n你地就踩到一文不值<br />\n<br />\n其實係你地眼中<br />\n係咪要中神通先叫成功<br />\n四絕都係廢物？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80f2b06caf165a6e97916b58e0c6ecb6e7e86f1f","tid":271101,"uid":1706,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:47:55.000Z","msg":"Too long<br />\n但係好同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6537eedb6be476f59af110e6bdc2f600208ebd0","tid":271101,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:50:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Too long<br />\n但係好同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d2a83e2b023debd53b402d0d18fec2e50202765","tid":271101,"uid":89182,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:55:01.000Z","msg":"連登細路好興唔鐘意一個人，就用佢性格強姦埋佢職業，幼稚到咁都唔知點認真講落去<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢d詞我普遍比7-9分，佢近年上水後d瘋瘋癲癲既行為（表面上都好），就無興趣欣賞。"},{"pid":"f3bff015553ba6f356b71c0295dbe93f3da6ac9f","tid":271101,"uid":85190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T20:57:04.000Z","msg":"而家D人連四大天王係邊個都唔知 識林敏聰係邊個已經好叻架啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/videos/1761367573880678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbeaconcollege.fans%2Fvideos%2F1761367573880678&d=FscGbLe7T1TTAA0VB6MmGARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9fa2a6af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/videos/1761367573880678</a>"},{"pid":"0f77e5c3fe1acf2c8d98ce4b22ec7cf697fe078b","tid":271101,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T21:01:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家D人連四大天王係邊個都唔知 識林敏聰係邊個已經好叻架啦<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/videos/1761367573880678\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbeaconcollege.fans%2Fvideos%2F1761367573880678&d=FscGbLe7T1TTAA0VB6MmGARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=9fa2a6af\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/beaconcollege.fans/videos/1761367573880678</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nTwins係90年代歌手都講得岀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fb4f16e35c15f695bce5002a7575440fea0f164","tid":271101,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:24:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登細路好興唔鐘意一個人，就用佢性格強姦埋佢職業，幼稚到咁都唔知點認真講落去<br />\n<br />\n利申：佢d詞我普遍比7-9分，佢近年上水後d瘋瘋癲癲既行為（表面上都好），就無興趣欣賞。</blockquote><br />\n佢都瘋癲咗廿幾年，分分鐘瘋癲時間仲大過你個年紀，點算近年呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"903ffbf02dc636d46776e0b1ea83443784139f03","tid":271101,"uid":89182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T01:44:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>連登細路好興唔