br />\n廿年前叫鬼馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家果d為左搵食，已經有d猥瑣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會以前叫鬼馬，依家叫猥瑣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪又係扮鄉音玩食字同講咸野問非所答，最大分別只係以前有人stop佢，依家D人唔敢"},{"pid":"1a1d7fdff4f2d284e833af07d6d0d041bfce208f","tid":271101,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T04:45:13.000Z","msg":"只係講佢生於逢時<br />\n如果佢係林生個代 比人秒啦"},{"pid":"54952eb076036633288d001fce5973887b5c468e","tid":271101,"uid":36341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T07:21:50.000Z","msg":"新一代最叻就推個果方面嘅權威出黎<br />\n去否定其他人嘅成就<br />\nEg 我靚仔<br />\n     新一代:你夠唔夠金城武靚仔<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa176fa8d9890e7309ea9c5cbcb164c3d160ad01","tid":271101,"uid":36715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T08:50:49.000Z","msg":"楊過：黃藥師只係一條教過我嘅契弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8675522045cbb58d5977a37501b372a5a2b2cc4","tid":271101,"uid":45147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T14:46:52.000Z","msg":"真心講一句，起碼佢有自己風格，詞有自己一套既畫面感<br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得好似首無心睡眠咁，&quot;張開口似救生圈實驗雨的酸與甜&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&quot;，呢啲你可以話唔係好似林夕個啲乜好玄既詞，但成個畫面好跳脫，幾得意&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n林夕填快歌填左今期流行添啦，話林敏聰冇料真係講唔過去"},{"pid":"735a76910b3ebcad0faf5abfa364e14143da6271","tid":271101,"uid":28355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-05T16:47:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cIY6pe7mZ7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcIY6pe7mZ7c&d=FscGbLe7T1TTAA0VB6MmGARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=26a30573\" data-auto-link target=\"_b